Running Total per Category
From the category_sales table, compute a running total of amount within each category separately, ordered by sale_date. Show: category, sale_date, amount, and running_total.

select category, sale_date, sum(amount) over 
(partition by category order by sale_date) as running_total_amount
from category_sales

