Q5. Running Total Reset per Month
From the transactions table, compute a running total of amount that resets at the start of each month. Show: txn_date, amount, and monthly_running_total


select *, sum(amount) over (PARTITION BY strftime('%Y-%m', txn_date) 
    ORDER BY txn_date
  ) as monthly_running_total
from transactions
